@startuml

actor User
participant "App Server" as App
database "jobs table" as DB
participant "Queue Worker" as Worker
participant "SMTP Server" as SMTP

User -> App: Create Order
App -> DB: Insert Order
App -> DB: Insert Job (SendOrderCreatedEmail)
App --> User: Return success response

== Worker Process ==

Worker -> DB: Fetch next job
Worker -> SMTP: Send email (Attempt #1)
SMTP --> Worker: Timeout / Error

Worker -> Worker: Wait 10 seconds (backoff[0])
Worker -> DB: Release job back to queue

Worker -> DB: Fetch job again
Worker -> SMTP: Send email (Attempt #2)
SMTP --> Worker: Temporary failure

Worker -> Worker: Wait 30 seconds (backoff[1])
Worker -> DB: Release job back to queue

Worker -> DB: Fetch job again
Worker -> SMTP: Send email (Attempt #3)
SMTP --> Worker: Success

Worker -> DB: Delete job from queue
Worker -> App: Log success

@enduml
